title: Bug 114470 - Error message throws when using new Date("3/2/2005") as value in table filter.
description: When using the value new Date("3/2/2005") as a filter in a table, an error message is being thrown.
OB: When using new Date("3/2/2005") as a value in the table filter, an error message is thrown.
EB: When using new Date("3/2/2005") as a value in the table filter, there should be no error message.
SR:
1. Open the application.
2. Navigate to the table filter.
3. Enter the value new Date("3/2/2005") into the filter.
4. Observe if any error message is displayed.
